00:21:39,618 --> 00:21:41,400
and you know what your audience wants.

456
00:21:43,044 --> 00:21:48,446
So for Telltale, just quickly, we had sort of a 90 to 120 minute experience,

457
00:21:48,446 --> 00:21:51,667
and every episode ended with a big cliffhanger.

