00:44:59,589 --> 00:45:00,730
Look at this.

942
00:45:00,730 --> 00:45:02,131
Look at this thing.

943
00:45:02,131 --> 00:45:04,073
It explains exactly what I'm talking about.

944
00:45:04,073 --> 00:45:09,957
I didn't even need to say anything.

945
00:45:09,957 --> 00:45:13,180
So yeah, back to the circle.

946
00:45:13,180 --> 00:45:15,702
It starts with you, it starts with emotional stories,

947
00:45:15,702 --> 00:45:19,345
character relationships, participatory art,

948
00:45:19,345 --> 00:45:21,987
compelling choices, and then on the other side,

949
00:45:21,987 --> 00:45:24,249
you've got the players, and they're gonna give back to you.

950
00:45:24,249 --> 00:45:27,391
You have to give to them and make it the circle.

951
00:45:29,658 --> 00:45:35,042
because you're going to get that connection and you want to build to this relationship.

952
00:45:35,042 --> 00:45:41,366
Over time, you want to build up to this relationship. And of course, you want to build

953
00:45:41,366 --> 00:45:53,314
to the payoff cat. So important. So that is my presentation. And thank you.

954
00:45:56,073 --> 00:45:58,274
We have some time for Q&A.

