00:47:38,667 --> 00:47:40,868
that we're trying to create and that over time,

985
00:47:41,608 --> 00:47:45,390
you start to churn people out because they're just like,

986
00:47:45,390 --> 00:47:47,050
well, I just don't believe the story anymore,

987
00:47:47,050 --> 00:47:47,490
I'm not into it.

